ADSL.AGEGR1N.comment: AGEGR1 = 1 if AGE <65. AGEGR1 = 2 if AGE 65-80. AGEGR1 = 3 if AGE >80.

ADSL.ITTFL.comment: Y if ARMCD ne ' '. N otherwise

ADSL.COMP16FL.comment: Y if subject has a SV.VISITNUM=10 and ENDDT>=date of visit 10, N otherwise

ADSL.COMP24FL.comment: Y if subject has a SV.VISITNUM=12 and ENDDT>= date of visit 12 , N otherwise

If both the month and day are missing no imputation is performed as these dates clearly indicate a start prior to the beginning of treatment. There are no events with completely missing start dates.
